Package org.nnsoft.guice.lifegycle

Objects lifecycle management made easy with Google Guice.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DisposeHandler
    A DisposeHandler instance is used to track dispose progress.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AfterInjectionModule
    Guice module to register methods to be invoked after injection is complete.
    DisposeModule
    Guice module to register methods to be invoked when Disposer.dispose() is invoked.
    Disposer
    A Disposer is a mini-container that releases resources invoking injectees methods annotated by Dispose.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AfterInjection
    The AfterInjection annotation is used on a method that needs to be executed after dependency injection is done to perform any initialization.
    Dispose
    The method annotated with Dispose is typically used to release resources that it has been holding.
